categories: Category:Jedi Masters of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: Mott Corbet was a male Jedi Master of the Jedi Order. Within the sacred Jedi texts, Corbet wrote of his dictum "what is, is without."
Corbet and his dictum were both originally mentioned briefly in George Lucas's rough draft as part of Deak Starkiller's Jedi-Bendu education.
